WEBVTT

01:11.028 --> 01:12.280
Whoo!

01:14.031 --> 01:16.993
I can't miss.

01:17.034 --> 01:18.869
You gotta get yourself
one of these, buddy.

01:18.911 --> 01:21.497
Let me see that son of a bitch.

01:21.539 --> 01:23.749
I tell ya,
them fuckin' Germans...

01:23.791 --> 01:26.377
Boy, they know how to make
a fuckin' gun, don't they?

01:26.419 --> 01:28.754
It's Italian. Yeah, whatever.

01:28.796 --> 01:30.881
Finish your beer and
hang it up. I feel hot.

01:32.592 --> 01:34.260
All right.

01:47.273 --> 01:51.110
Hey, I got an easy shot for you.

01:51.152 --> 01:53.279
Christ, you know better than
to point that fuckin' thing at me.

01:53.321 --> 01:55.489
I hear you been sleepin'
with my wife!

01:57.408 --> 01:59.577
- Who told you that?
- Amanda!

01:59.619 --> 02:01.662
Amanda. That's right.

02:03.247 --> 02:05.750
Now, why... why would she
say something like that?

02:05.791 --> 02:08.169
What?

02:08.210 --> 02:09.669
I want to know.

02:09.711 --> 02:12.131
I don't think that matters
right now, Clay.

02:12.173 --> 02:14.008
I don't believe she
told you. What are you...

02:14.050 --> 02:15.468
Well, she did...

02:15.509 --> 02:20.389
In great detail,
Mr. Like to Do it from Behind.

02:20.431 --> 02:22.516
You know, Earl, this...
This is fucking crazy.

02:22.558 --> 02:25.227
I don't know what Amanda's
been telling you or why...

02:25.269 --> 02:28.189
I don't think you appreciate the
seriousness of this conversation!

02:28.230 --> 02:29.732
Goddamn it!

02:29.774 --> 02:32.276
Now...

02:32.318 --> 02:34.236
Come on, Earl. You're...

02:34.278 --> 02:36.697
You're not gonna shoot me. No?

02:36.739 --> 02:39.575
Now, I know you, buddy. And...

02:39.617 --> 02:41.911
You can't kill a deer, so just...

02:41.952 --> 02:44.580
Put the gun down.

02:44.622 --> 02:48.000
Just... Put it down.

02:51.003 --> 02:52.213
You're right.

02:52.254 --> 02:54.090
The fact is...

02:57.301 --> 02:59.720
you're gonna shoot me.

02:59.762 --> 03:01.764
Now I'm a little confused.

03:01.806 --> 03:03.766
I can't stop thinkin'
about it, Clay.

03:03.808 --> 03:05.601
Ever since she told me.

03:05.643 --> 03:08.062
She was a virgin
when we was married.

03:08.104 --> 03:11.399
Nah. I remember her being
a little wild in high school.

03:11.440 --> 03:13.776
You're straying!
Now pick up the gun!

03:13.818 --> 03:17.488
You know, you're making
way too much of this.

03:17.530 --> 03:21.242
I mean, we're both a little too
fuckin' drunk. Let's sober up a little.

03:21.283 --> 03:23.828
This is a little out of fuckin' control,
don't you think?

03:23.869 --> 03:26.914
I can't have the whole goddamn
town knowin' what happened!

03:26.956 --> 03:29.166
And it ain't easy for me,
you bein' my best friend and all,

03:29.166 --> 03:31.252
but you're gon' pay,
you son of a bitch.

03:31.293 --> 03:33.504
Not with your life,
but you're gonna do some time.

03:33.546 --> 03:35.297
That's for sure.

03:35.339 --> 03:37.299
Now, Earl...

03:37.341 --> 03:40.010
You're... You're a
little out of it right now.

03:40.052 --> 03:44.181
- Yeah, you think so?
- You're a little out of your mind.

03:46.183 --> 03:48.978
- Right now, yes, you're a little fuckin' crazy.
- Oh, yeah? Crazy?

03:49.019 --> 03:51.480
Crazy enough to tell people we
was comin' up here shootin' today?

03:51.522 --> 03:54.358
Crazy enough to tell Amanda that
me and you was gonna have it out...

03:54.400 --> 03:56.444
over this here very issue?

03:56.485 --> 03:59.029
Crazy enough to bring
both of the trucks up here?

03:59.071 --> 04:01.073
'Cause it'll be one thing
to hide my body.

04:01.115 --> 04:03.367
It's gon' be another thing getting
both these trucks outta here.

04:04.493 --> 04:08.247
I thought it all out, Clay.

04:08.289 --> 04:10.124
Now be a man
and pick up the gun.

04:10.166 --> 04:12.877
Earl, I'm not gonna
pick up the gun.

04:14.420 --> 04:16.464
Earl.

04:16.505 --> 04:18.632
Good luck explaining me dying
with a bullet from your gun, buddy.

04:18.673 --> 04:20.926
Put the gun down.

04:20.968 --> 04:22.553
I bet you don't think
I got the nerve, do ya?

04:22.595 --> 04:23.971
You got the nerve.
You got the fuckin' nerve!

04:24.013 --> 04:26.348
But you're scaring
the shit out of me!

04:26.390 --> 04:28.225
Jesus Christ!

04:31.228 --> 04:33.439
Earl! Put the fucking gun down!

04:33.481 --> 04:36.108
That's gonna rule out
the suicide angle, lover boy!

04:36.150 --> 04:38.194
It's not worth it!
She doesn't mean shit to me!

04:38.235 --> 04:40.112
I don't fucking care about her!

04:40.154 --> 04:41.906
Just don't fucking do this!

04:41.947 --> 04:44.116
No!

04:49.079 --> 04:50.790
What are you doin'?

04:50.831 --> 04:52.958
She's not worth it!

04:53.000 --> 04:55.920
She's not fuckin' worth it!

05:02.468 --> 05:05.137
♪

05:15.606 --> 05:18.984
♪ I've got a time bomb
in my mind, Mom ♪

05:19.026 --> 05:21.612
♪ I hear it tickin',
but I don't know why ♪

05:21.654 --> 05:25.616
♪ I'd call the police,
but they don't like me ♪

05:25.658 --> 05:28.661
♪ I hear 'em whispering
when I walk by ♪

05:28.702 --> 05:32.122
♪ Uh-huh ♪

05:32.164 --> 05:35.751
♪ Ooh-ooh ♪

05:35.793 --> 05:39.213
♪ I've got a land mine
in my bloodline ♪

05:39.255 --> 05:42.132
♪ I'm not immune
to gettin' blown apart ♪

05:42.174 --> 05:43.884
♪ She's like a claymore ♪

05:43.926 --> 05:45.803
♪ That's what she's there for ♪

05:45.845 --> 05:48.931
♪ She's waitin' round here
to get blown apart ♪

05:48.973 --> 05:51.976
♪ Uh-huh ♪

05:52.017 --> 05:54.979
♪ Having her on my brain's
like gettin' hit by a train ♪

05:55.020 --> 05:56.605
♪ She's gonna kill me ♪

05:56.647 --> 06:00.025
♪ Oh, Celeste ♪

06:00.067 --> 06:08.075
♪ Oh, Celeste ♪

06:08.325 --> 06:15.416
♪ Oh, Celeste ♪

06:55.748 --> 06:58.334
Crazy son of a bitch.

07:00.002 --> 07:02.296
There's more.

07:02.338 --> 07:04.506
What do you mean
there's more? Hmm?

07:04.548 --> 07:06.383
How can there be more?

07:06.383 --> 07:08.677
You're not gonna
believe this, but, uh,

07:10.387 --> 07:12.598
he set it up to make it
look like I did it.

07:15.768 --> 07:18.062
And why the hell
would he do that? Hmm?

07:18.103 --> 07:20.481
Because of you and me.

07:22.191 --> 07:23.859
You can leave me out of this.

07:27.279 --> 07:29.448
Leave you out of this?

07:29.490 --> 07:31.408
Amanda, I need your help.

07:31.408 --> 07:33.410
That's the only way
anybody will believe me.

07:33.410 --> 07:35.537
I said leave me out of it!

07:37.206 --> 07:40.000
Don't do this to me. Not now.

07:40.042 --> 07:42.586
Look, I want nothin'
to do with it, all right?

07:42.628 --> 07:45.130
I can't have people
all over town talkin' about us.

07:45.172 --> 07:48.467
Jesus Christ, Amanda.
Because of us, Earl...

07:48.509 --> 07:50.970
Look, the crazy motherfucker got what he wanted,
it sounds like to me.

07:51.011 --> 07:52.638
I'm sorry, Clay,

07:52.680 --> 07:57.101
and I do hope it turns out
all right and all that.

07:57.142 --> 08:00.354
But as far as I'm concerned,

08:00.396 --> 08:03.857
I didn't see you today
or any other day.

08:05.734 --> 08:07.152
I'll still tell them.

08:09.071 --> 08:11.198
Go ahead. I'll just deny it.

08:11.240 --> 08:14.243
I mean, who are they
gonna believe? Hmm?

08:15.619 --> 08:17.705
You or the widow?

08:17.746 --> 08:19.832
♪ Holy smoke Land sakes alive ♪

08:19.873 --> 08:22.292
♪ I never thought
this could happen to me ♪

08:22.334 --> 08:24.420
♪ Uh-huh, yeah ♪

08:26.171 --> 08:27.715
♪ Yeah ♪

08:27.756 --> 08:29.758
♪ I got stung
by a sweet honey bee ♪

08:29.800 --> 08:32.135
♪ Oh, what a feelin'
come over me ♪

08:32.177 --> 08:35.304
♪ it started in my eyes,
crept up to my head ♪

08:35.347 --> 08:37.140
♪ Flew to my heart
till I was stung dead ♪

08:37.182 --> 08:40.352
♪ I'm done, uh-huh,
I got stung ♪

08:40.394 --> 08:42.145
♪

08:42.187 --> 08:44.690
♪ Uh-huh, yeah ♪

08:44.732 --> 08:47.151
♪ Uh-huh, yeah ♪

08:47.192 --> 08:49.695
♪ She had all that I wanted
and more ♪

08:49.737 --> 08:51.905
♪ And I've seen honey bees
before ♪

08:51.947 --> 08:53.407
♪ She started buzzin'
in my ear ♪

08:53.449 --> 08:54.992
♪ Buzzin' in my brain ♪

08:55.034 --> 08:57.077
♪ Got stung all over,
but I feel no pain ♪

08:57.119 --> 08:58.871
♪ I'm done, uh-huh ♪

08:58.912 --> 09:02.166
♪ I got stung ♪

09:02.207 --> 09:04.668
♪ Now, don't think
I'm complainin' ♪

09:04.710 --> 09:06.920
♪ I'm mighty pleased we met ♪

09:06.962 --> 09:09.840
♪ 'Cause you give me one little
peck on the back of my neck ♪

09:09.882 --> 09:12.176
♪ And I break out
in a cold, cold sweat ♪

09:12.217 --> 09:14.344
♪ Well, if I live
to be a hundred and two ♪

09:14.386 --> 09:16.847
♪ I won't let nobody sting me
but you ♪

09:16.889 --> 09:18.307
♪ I'll keep buzzin'... ♪

09:46.001 --> 09:48.087
Oh, god-fuckin'-damn it.

10:00.057 --> 10:03.936
You want to catch that, Barney?

10:03.977 --> 10:06.522
Barney!

10:11.276 --> 10:14.404
Sheriff's Station. Mooney here.

10:14.446 --> 10:16.240
It's all burnt to hell.

10:20.410 --> 10:22.329
Let's get around the other side.

10:27.126 --> 10:31.171
He went off right over there?

10:31.213 --> 10:32.881
Yeah, over there.

10:36.593 --> 10:39.179
That's his boot sittin'
on the transmission.

10:39.221 --> 10:40.889
Tell me the truth, Clay.

10:44.143 --> 10:45.894
Was he drinking?

10:48.147 --> 10:50.274
Mooney, it's Sunday.

10:50.315 --> 10:51.900
Yeah.

10:53.443 --> 10:56.196
You ever know Earl
to be sober on a Sunday?

10:58.198 --> 11:01.660
Whoo! Ain't a whole
hell of a lot left.

11:01.702 --> 11:03.579
You want me to call the coroner?

11:04.830 --> 11:07.624
He's in Wyoming, fishing.

11:09.459 --> 11:11.086
Well, we gotta call somebody.

11:12.629 --> 11:15.465
To tell us what?

11:15.507 --> 11:17.593
I always knew that
drunken son of a bitch...

11:17.634 --> 11:20.012
was gonna kill himself one day.

11:27.603 --> 11:31.815
"And I will dwell in the house
of the Lord forever.

11:31.857 --> 11:35.027
Ashes to ashes, dust to dust."

12:13.023 --> 12:15.817
How about
gettin' me one, cowboy?

12:21.823 --> 12:23.867
Where's your car?

12:23.909 --> 12:25.661
In the garage.

12:25.702 --> 12:27.746
Gotta keep up appearances, baby.

12:27.788 --> 12:29.456
What are you doing here?

12:29.498 --> 12:33.210
What do you mean?
It's Wednesday.

12:33.252 --> 12:35.337
So what?

12:35.379 --> 12:38.590
So we always do it on Wednesday.

12:38.632 --> 12:41.718
- You can't be serious.
- Why not?

12:41.718 --> 12:45.347
Amanda, the body
isn't even cold yet.

12:49.184 --> 12:50.894
Yeah, well...

12:50.936 --> 12:52.688
It got too hot to ever get cold.

12:52.729 --> 12:54.523
You saw to that,
didn't you, cowboy?

12:55.941 --> 12:59.069
- Shut up.
- Mmm.

12:59.111 --> 13:01.071
I'm just teasing you, baby.

13:01.113 --> 13:03.240
I must say you impressed me
though, Clay.

13:03.282 --> 13:07.327
It was pretty, um, slick
the way you handled that.

13:07.369 --> 13:09.121
Yeah, well, I wouldn't
have had to...

13:09.162 --> 13:11.081
if you'd just told
the fuckin' truth.

13:11.123 --> 13:13.917
Mmm, now don't start.

13:13.959 --> 13:17.129
I just...
didn't know what to do.

13:17.170 --> 13:22.426
I figured it'd be better if you did
the thinking for both of us. Hmm?

13:22.467 --> 13:24.261
Now come on.

13:24.303 --> 13:27.764
Kick off those boots
and come to mama.

13:29.016 --> 13:31.601
What is wrong with you?

13:31.643 --> 13:34.521
What do you mean,
what the fuck is wrong with me?

13:34.563 --> 13:36.773
He's dead! We don't have to sneak around anymore,
baby.

13:36.773 --> 13:39.651
We can do whatever
the fuck we want.

13:39.693 --> 13:42.321
Do you not get it?

13:42.362 --> 13:44.114
Earl killed himself over you.

13:44.156 --> 13:46.241
So what? He was crazy.

13:47.326 --> 13:48.702
I mean it.

13:50.746 --> 13:53.790
You will be, too,
if you try and make any more out of it than that.

13:53.790 --> 13:55.250
Now...

13:57.252 --> 13:59.629
Come on. Come on.

13:59.671 --> 14:02.716
We can use the video
camera. Come on.

14:02.758 --> 14:07.262
You know,
we are not just gonna pick up where we left off.

14:08.597 --> 14:10.766
I mean, people would talk.

14:11.808 --> 14:13.769
And I know how you hate that.

14:14.936 --> 14:17.522
Fine.

14:17.564 --> 14:20.692
But I ain't waitin' long, Clay.

14:20.734 --> 14:23.612
I'm a single fuckin' woman now,

14:23.653 --> 14:26.406
and this town ain't exactly blessed
with eligible fuckin' bachelors.

14:29.368 --> 14:32.454
We never made any plans,
you and I. Never.

14:33.705 --> 14:35.999
Yeah.

14:36.041 --> 14:37.459
Maybe not.

14:39.711 --> 14:41.838
But there's a bond between us.

14:41.838 --> 14:44.132
Earl saw to that.

14:44.174 --> 14:45.801
Now zip me.

14:54.768 --> 14:57.104
♪

15:00.524 --> 15:03.276
♪ I'm wanted in 50 states
and in Mexico ♪

15:03.318 --> 15:05.862
Hey, slick. Oh, hey, Glen.

15:05.862 --> 15:08.198
How about a game?

15:08.240 --> 15:10.450
I don't know. Come on, man.

15:10.492 --> 15:13.829
I got no competition here.

15:13.870 --> 15:16.289
You want some competition?
I want some competition.

15:17.582 --> 15:18.834
All right.

15:22.879 --> 15:25.382
- Too good.
- Well, it was an easy shot.

15:25.424 --> 15:27.050
You're drinkin' Bud, right?

15:27.092 --> 15:28.510
You know it.

15:35.142 --> 15:37.686
Ever do it on a pool table?

15:40.355 --> 15:42.149
What are you doing here?

15:42.190 --> 15:46.570
Mmm. You aren't still sore,
are you? Hmm?

15:46.611 --> 15:50.323
Mmm. Let's just, uh,

15:51.616 --> 15:53.285
start fresh.

15:54.786 --> 15:56.872
We're not starting anything.

15:58.290 --> 16:00.208
You don't mean that.

16:01.460 --> 16:03.712
Excuse me.

16:03.753 --> 16:08.425
You're forgettin' how...
good I can make you feel.

16:08.467 --> 16:12.095
Keep your hands off me.

16:12.137 --> 16:15.557
Ooh, someone's touchy. Hmm?

16:17.309 --> 16:19.019
It's been a while, hasn't it,

16:19.060 --> 16:24.274
since you done it
with a... real woman?

16:24.316 --> 16:27.277
And I know
all the buttons to push.

16:27.319 --> 16:29.905
Don't I, cowboy? Hmm?

16:36.828 --> 16:38.246
Damn it.

16:40.332 --> 16:45.212
Amanda, why can't you
just leave me alone?

16:46.963 --> 16:49.132
You made a big mistake, cowboy.

16:52.093 --> 16:53.303
Amanda.

16:53.345 --> 16:55.347
Fuck you!

16:56.765 --> 16:58.517
Is this table open?

17:04.981 --> 17:07.901
Don't hit me or nothin'.
Just wanna play pool.

17:09.402 --> 17:12.405
That was a nice break.

17:12.446 --> 17:14.199
Guess you're solids.

17:14.241 --> 17:16.451
And you're gonna stay solids.
Nice shot.

17:16.492 --> 17:18.411
I knew a guy
growin' up named Stuff.

17:18.453 --> 17:20.664
They called him that 'cause
he put so much stuff on the ball.

17:20.704 --> 17:22.457
Oh, yeah. Shooter's line.

17:25.126 --> 17:27.378
Lot of people start off hot.
I'm kind of the fireman.

17:27.420 --> 17:29.172
I cool 'em down a little bit.

17:29.214 --> 17:30.632
Good shot.

17:33.927 --> 17:35.720
When you're done,
maybe I'll just shoot mine out.

17:35.762 --> 17:37.347
Just for the fun of it.
You know what I mean?

17:37.389 --> 17:38.974
Just kinda see how I do.

17:41.017 --> 17:43.019
Last shot right here.
For the game.

17:51.236 --> 17:53.029
Whoo. Man.

17:53.029 --> 17:55.031
You're a fuckin' shark, you are.

17:55.031 --> 17:57.409
I put enough damn quarters
in this table. I should be.

17:57.450 --> 17:59.369
Goddamn right, I guess.

17:59.411 --> 18:01.871
How about I buy you a beer, man?

18:01.913 --> 18:03.999
- Not gonna say no.
- All right.

18:04.040 --> 18:06.293
- I didn't catch your name or anything.
- Oh, Clay.

18:06.334 --> 18:08.795
I'm Lester Long. Lester,
good to meet you.

18:08.837 --> 18:11.756
Lester the, uh, molester.

18:11.798 --> 18:15.719
Couple beers comin' up.
Sharpshooter.

18:15.760 --> 18:17.554
♪

18:17.596 --> 18:19.055
Let me tell ya.

18:19.055 --> 18:21.725
It was two feet long
if it was an inch.

18:21.766 --> 18:24.978
- Goddamn.
- And still I had to throw the damn thing back.

18:25.020 --> 18:27.814
Now tell me, what the hell
was the point of that?

18:27.856 --> 18:31.109
Personally, I never went for all
that "catch and release" bullshit.

18:31.151 --> 18:32.944
You know what I mean?

18:32.986 --> 18:35.071
I mean, they got all this fuckin'
fancy equipment nowadays,

18:35.071 --> 18:39.576
but what the fuck is it worth
if you can't fuckin' keep it?

18:39.618 --> 18:41.870
Why don't you just smoke
a filterless cigarette?

18:41.911 --> 18:44.914
I like it this way.

18:44.956 --> 18:47.834
- So, you get out much?
- Yeah, all the time, man.

18:47.876 --> 18:49.794
I been fishin' since
I was three years old.

18:49.836 --> 18:51.880
Three years old?

18:51.921 --> 18:53.715
I love... I love fishin'.

18:56.092 --> 18:57.927
I guess there's no wedding bells
in the future for you...

18:57.969 --> 18:59.763
and that little miss
that walked in here tonight.

18:59.804 --> 19:01.931
No, no, no. Come on.
The night was so good.

19:01.973 --> 19:03.642
Let's not talk about her.

19:03.683 --> 19:07.604
I gotta tell you, man.
She looked pretty fine to me.

19:07.646 --> 19:09.689
I had my eye on her
the minute she walked in.

19:09.731 --> 19:11.650
Well, you're new in town.
You don't know any better.

19:11.691 --> 19:14.653
Let me tell you something.
You take my advice.

19:14.694 --> 19:16.488
Steer clear of Amanda.

19:16.529 --> 19:18.948
I tell you one thing though.

19:18.990 --> 19:20.575
You sure handled her right, man.

19:20.617 --> 19:22.494
Goddamn it.

19:22.535 --> 19:24.537
Shouldn't have hit her.

19:26.373 --> 19:29.834
Well, you got your point
across, didn't you?

19:29.876 --> 19:32.879
Come on. To your health.

19:32.921 --> 19:36.925
Well, I'm all out, but, uh...

19:36.966 --> 19:38.885
What the hell.

19:41.304 --> 19:42.514
Thanks.

19:42.555 --> 19:45.016
Sure took you
long enough to ask.

19:45.058 --> 19:47.602
♪ I guess I haven't been
getting out much lately.

19:47.644 --> 19:50.438
Oh, I forgot about Earl.

19:50.480 --> 19:52.273
That was real sad.

19:53.858 --> 19:55.694
Yeah.

19:55.735 --> 19:58.780
You know, Amanda sure seems
to be taking it well.

20:00.615 --> 20:02.367
What do you mean?
You should see her.

20:02.409 --> 20:05.954
She walks around town like...
Like nothin' happened.

20:05.995 --> 20:11.167
I just suppose different people
handle things in different ways.

20:12.919 --> 20:14.421
Thanks.

20:19.050 --> 20:21.803
I don't like to talk bad
about people,

20:21.845 --> 20:24.848
but I just never understood how
Earl could've married a bitch like that.

20:27.350 --> 20:28.852
Ooh.

